There is no ReadMe in the file.

*Note
All the credits goes to me (AppleJuiceBox). I am also called AppleJuice on counter-strike: source. Do not publish the map on another website without my permission. (I know you won't)

*About the map
I made this map in 2007. It's my first map so forgive me if you find some glitches or bugs. While playing it, you will discover:

-A huge maze with secrets
-2 ways of reaching the top, easy and pro
-Hidden guns, teleports, and more
-Spikes you must dodge to reach the top
-Much more
